<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-10-06T08:48:07-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-10-06T08:48:07-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-06T08:48:07-04:00</updated><title> X 正在测试新的付费会员级别，以弥补广告收入不佳的情况</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 X 徽标的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sDJO7y8UwsRHODVl9c4HV4nzZq4=/1x0:3001x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/72727404/STK160_X_Twitter_005.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;免费会员计划可能很快就会被完全删除。&lt;/em>; |插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Lml7rH&quot;>;X（前身为 Twitter）正在寻求将其高级订阅服务分为三个会员级别，允许该公司根据广告数量改变订阅价格显示给用户。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-05/x-tells-bankers-that-advertisers-are-back-but-spending-less?leadSource=uverify%20wall&amp;amp ;sref=ExbtjcSG&quot;>;据&lt;em>;彭博社消息人士&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;称，该公司目前正在测试 Basic、Standard 和 Plus 版本，该消息人士参​​加了周四与 X 以及帮助 Musk 融资收购的债权人的电话会议现有高级计划的一部分，目前起价为&lt;a href=&quot;https://help.twitter.com/en/using-x/x-premium&quot;>;每月 8 美元&lt;/a>;。目前尚不清楚免费版本是否会继续存在。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;joEFjt&quot;>;尚未公布新会员级别的定价信息。不过，根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/aaronp613/status/1710060481296105874&quot;>;之前在 X 应用中发现的详细信息&lt;/a>;，入门级 Basic 套餐不会减少广告数量用户在...上看到...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23906000/x-twitter-new-paid-membership-tiers-ad -收入&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23906000/x-twitter-new-paid-membership-tiers-ad-revenue" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23906000/x-twitter-new-paid-membership-tiers-ad-revenue</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-06T08:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-06T08:30:00-04:00</updated><title>在重大软件更新之前购买 Google Pixel Buds Pro 可节省 65 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 的 Pixel Buds Pro 耳机，黄色柠檬草色，放在桌面上白色充电盒的底部。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/u2AXRhZUIMT_n82MoK-uD022WX0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72727381/DSCF8502.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Pixel Buds Pro 将在未来几周内获得包含新功能的软件更新。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;8DNfBC&quot;>;这一周都是 Google 新闻，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23902026 /google-pixel-8-launch-event-biggest-announcements-watch-buds-pro&quot;>;公告阶段&lt;/a>;甚至&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23869483/us-v -google-search-antitrust-case-updates&quot;>;在法庭&lt;/a>;。而 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23902229/google-pixel-8-hands-on-specs-price-release-date&quot;>;Pixel 8&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/23900556/google-pixel-8-pro-hands-on-specs-price-launch&quot;>;Pixel 8 Pro&lt;/a>; 可能在 &lt;a href 上受到了很多关注=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/4/23895660/google-pixel-8-event-news-roundup&quot;>;Made by Google 主题演讲&lt;/a>;，Google 还宣布了相当大的&lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/4/23901261/google-pixel-buds-pro-colors-conversation-detection&quot;>;Pixel Buds Pro 即将推出软件更新&lt;/a>;，其中包括自动更新对话检测和增加的语音通话带宽。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Zmf7rP&quot;>;对于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23281445/google-pixel- buds-pro-noise-canceling-earbuds-review&quot;>;&lt;strong>;Pixel Buds Pro&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>; 价格降至新低。您可以获得 Google 旗舰无线耳机 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wellbots.com%2Fproducts%2Fgoogle-pixel- buds-pro-headphones&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F10%2F6%2F23904491%2Fgoogle-pixel-buds-pro-nest-doorbell-floodlight-apple- watch-se-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;10 月之前结帐时使用代码 &lt;strong>;VERGE65&lt;/strong>;，在 Wellbots 仅需 134.99 美元&lt;/a>;（折扣 65 美元） 11日。 Pixel Buds Pro 是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds&quot;>;您现在可以买到的最好的耳机&lt;/a>;之一，特别是如果您是 Pixel手机所有者并希望利用独家功能，例如...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23904491/google-pixel-buds- pro-nest-doorbell-floodlight-apple-watch-se-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23904491/google-pixel-buds-pro-nest-doorbell-floodlight-apple-watch-se-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23904491/google-pixel-buds-pro-nest-doorbell-floodlight-apple-watch-se-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-06T06:07:30-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-06T06:07:30-04:00</updated><title> Google 的放大镜辅助功能应用程序已准备好下载到 Pixel 手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三部手机显示 Google Pixel 手机的放大镜应用。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/F77Zn_ytY3UIfiMo3z3RUwD0fZs=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72727069/Google_Pixel_Magnifier.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;放大镜包含一些额外的辅助功能优势，而不仅仅是简单地放大远处的文本。&lt;/em>; |图片：Google&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;X7Bwq6&quot;>;Google 发布了适用于 Pixel 手机的放大镜应用，旨在使小、光线昏暗或远处的文本更易于阅读。新的无障碍应用在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23902229/google-pixel-8-hands-on-specs-price-release-date&quot;>;Pixel 8 系列&lt;/a>;上首次亮相&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/4/23895660/google-pixel-8-event-news-roundup&quot;>;本周早些时候的 Google Pixel 活动&lt;/a>;中介绍了这一点，以及根据放大镜应用程序 &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/ store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.accessibility.magnifier&quot;>;Play 商品详情&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;JNKSyn&quot;>;Pixel 5 手机或稍后，但根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5google.com/2023/10/05/google-pixel-magnifier-app/&quot;>;9to5Google，这不包括 Pixel Fold 或 Pixel Tablet 设备&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。该应用程序本身具有相当简单的用户界面。默认屏幕包括用于控制缩放功能的大 + 和 - 按钮，位于...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905966 /google-pixel-magnifier-accessibility-app-zoom-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905966/google-pixel-magnifier-accessibility-app-zoom-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905966/google-pixel-magnifier-accessibility-app-zoom-release-date</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-06T06:00:05-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-06T06:00:05-04:00</updated><title>微软计划下周完成与动视暴雪的巨额交易</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Xbox 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8zSjgdneJ1pZd1DIFQ6gqDR5aqc=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72727055/acastro_STK048_04.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;aBoBHm&quot;>;微软计划下周敲定其以 687 亿美元收购动视暴雪的提议。一位熟悉微软计划的消息人士告诉 &lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>;，该公司将 10 月 13 日星期五作为截止日期，届时它将向全世界宣布为期 20 个月的购买《使命召唤》的流程&lt;em>; /em>;制造商动视暴雪已经结束了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Cml9kL&quot;>;不过，该日期仍将取决于英国竞争和市场管理局，该监管机构今年早些时候阻止了微软的交易。微软最近&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/22/23828302/microsoft-activision-blizzard-acquisition-ubisoft-cloud-gaming-rights-uk-cma&quot;>;重组了交易&lt; /a>; 将动视暴雪当前和新游戏的云游戏版权转让给育碧，Xbox 制造商获得了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/22/23885176/microsofts-activision- blizzard-uk-cma-preliminary-approval&quot;>;上个月底获得了 CMA 的初步批准&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;uWoxPE&quot;>;CMA 的截止日期已到期...&lt; /p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905946/microsoft-activision-blizzard-deal-finalization-timing-cma&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905946/microsoft-activision-blizzard-deal-finalization-timing-cma" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905946/microsoft-activision-blizzard-deal-finalization-timing-cma</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-06T04:33:02-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-06T04:33:02-04:00</updated><title> 《寂静岭：升天》将于万圣节首映</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;两个人影走过结冰的湖面，下面有恶魔的存在。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/CM5QC_iQR8iXjqscJTV5_md9HtE=/0x0:1080x720/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72726948/maxresdefault__2_.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Genvid&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3jglbm&quot;>;&lt;em>;寂静岭：升天&lt;/em>;，以经典恐怖游戏宇宙为背景的互动流媒体系列，将有该游戏的执行制作人兼开发商 Genvid 首席执行官 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SHAscension/status/1710060757134586347&quot;>;Jacob Navok&lt;/a>; 表示，该游戏将于美国东部时间 10 月 31 日晚上 9 点“全球首发”。如果您想参加，可以通过 Ascension 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/silent-hill-ascension/id6468639920 &quot;>;iOS&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.genvid.shascension&amp;amp;hl=en_US&quot;>;Android&lt;/a>; 应用，或者访问 &lt;a href=&quot;https://ascension.com/&quot;>;Ascension.com&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;kCeEqt&quot;>;“我故意使用‘全球首映’这个词，因为《寂静岭：升天》不是一款游戏，”纳沃克解释道。 “这是一个流媒体系列节目，你作为观众，可以现场参与以确定会发生什么。你和社区的其他成员将决定角色的命运。”然而，这并不意味着《Ascension》是真人版。这非常像一个&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23742245/silent-hill-ascension-trailer-konami-genvid&quot;>;视频游戏......&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905933/silent-hill-ascension-release-date-october-31st-halloween&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905933/silent-hill-ascension-release-date-october-31st-halloween" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/6/23905933/silent-hill-ascension-release-date-october-31st-halloween</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T20:29:22-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T20:29:22-04:00</updated><title>萨姆·班克曼-弗里德的豆袋椅也是一个谎言吗？</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Sam Bankman-Fried 在货币符号和箭头图形背景上的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/i3chxcTPvTjtdSXqYA4xi1Cb9AQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72726363/236817_SBF_Trial_Stock_CVirginia_C .0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;仔细选择你的大学室友... |照片插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 提供 |摄影：Drew Angerer，Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Bankman-Fried 麻省理工学院的两名室友为起诉提出了严厉的指控。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905665/sam-bankman-fried-fraud-trial-wang-yedidia-testimony&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905665/sam-bankman-fried-fraud-trial-wang-yedidia-testimony" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905665/sam-bankman-fried-fraud-trial-wang-yedidia-testimony</id><author><name>伊丽莎白·洛帕托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T19:52:36-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T19:52:36-04:00</updated><title>加拿大并没有试图压制播客</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;青色背景上一系列蓝色麦克风的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LwpupAymHIoODZdHivW41xpjNjs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72726262/VRG_Illo_STK427_K_Radtke_Getty_Mics .0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;克里斯汀·拉特克 / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;rrIVWq&quot;>;负责监督广播、电视和在线流媒体服务的加拿大监管机构发布了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.canada.ca/ en/radio-television-te communications/news/2023/09/crtc-takes-major-step-forward-to-modernize-canadas-broadcasting-framework.html&quot;>;上周关于一项具有挑衅性的新规则的新闻发布&lt;/a>; 。任何在加拿大运营、提供广播内容且年收入超过 1000 万加元的在线流媒体服务都需要在 11 月之前填写注册表。新闻稿称，这包括提供播客的在线服务。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EVo6ix&quot;>;此举在社交媒体和&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat. com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fopinion%2Farticle-the-crtcs-latest-regulatory-decision-is-sending-a-chill-through-the% 2F&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F10%2F5%2F23905644%2Fcanada-podcast-platform-registration-requirement&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot; _blank&quot;>;一些加拿大新闻媒体的专栏文章&lt;/a>;表明，该规则是政府控制播客言论的开始。加拿大广播电视和电信委员会 (CRTC) 的一位发言人告诉 Hot Pod&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2023/10/5/23905644/canada-podcast-platform-registration-requirement&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905644/canada-podcast-platform-registration-requirement" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905644/canada-podcast-platform-registration-requirement</id><author><name>阿姆丽塔·哈立德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T19:51:19-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T19:51:19-04:00</updated><title>以下是目前最优惠的 Apple Watch 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;用双击手势听写文本的人。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8XWQRQKzICMBInM3K-ogSPxoLx0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/66976955/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_ 0710.31.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple Watch Series 9 与之前的型号相比并不是一个巨大的进步，但它确实提供了一些新功能。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Vv1fRn&quot;>;&lt;em>;编者注：&lt;/em>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23903764 /amazon-october-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2023&quot;>;&lt;em>;亚马逊 10 月 Prime 会员日&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>;设置为 &lt;/em>;&lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/18/23878420/amazon-october-prime-day-big-deal-days-fall-dates&quot;>;&lt;em>;10 月 10 日开始&lt;/em>;&lt; /a>;&lt;em>;。幸运的是，如果您喜欢提前购物，我们已经汇总了 &lt;/em>;